    <a href="https://book.douban.com/reading/19100582/">第二章 清日战争观</a>
</li>

<li>
    <a href="https://book.douban.com/reading/19100653/">第三章 清日战争大事记</a>
</li>

<li>
    <a href="https://book.douban.com/reading/19100694/">结束语</a>
</li>
</ul>
