  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5398212">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5398212/" class="title-link">幽暗长廊的明朗挂图</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5398212"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/qdmimi19810920/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1392601-24.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qdmimi19810920/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小米=qdmimi</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-21"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-21 14:31:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5398212_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  可以确定的一件事情是，这是一本“不动声色”的资料书，从中几乎找不出比教科书尺度更大的感情表达段落，其内容大致是自日本国内收藏文献中梳理出的与甲午战争前后历史有关的文字、图像与表格。不过正因此种异于往常的角度，它的面世也具有了独特的价值，也许能够挤进研究者的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5398212/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">20有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5398212_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5398212_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7593139">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7593139/" class="title-link">写在阅兵前夕-关于《清日战争》</a>
